          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><html:p>Any <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000U.xml" title="biinverse" addr="forest://erct/erct-000U" type="local">biinvertible map</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001T.xml" title="n-truncated map" addr="forest://erct/erct-001T" type="local">propositional</fr:link>.</html:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-002W/0</fr:addr><fr:route>https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-002W/0.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="biinvertible maps are propositional › forest://erct/erct-002W/0"><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-002W.xml" title="biinvertible maps are propositional" addr="forest://erct/erct-002W" type="local"><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-000U.xml" title="biinverse" addr="forest://erct/erct-000U" type="local">biinvertible</fr:link> maps are <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001T.xml" title="n-truncated map" addr="forest://erct/erct-001T" type="local">propositional</fr:link></fr:link> › forest://erct/erct-002W/0</fr:title><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>We must show that each <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml" title="fiber" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">proposition</fr:link>; in fact, each <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml" title="fiber" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> is <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">contractible</fr:link> as <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-002N.xml" title="biinvertible maps are contractible" addr="forest://erct/erct-002N" type="local">biinvertible maps are contractible</fr:link>, and <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001K.xml" title="contractible types are propositions" addr="forest://erct/erct-001K" type="local">contractible types are propositions</fr:link>.</html:p>
